<body>
  <div class="wrapper">

    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand">LoanDesk &mdash; Application Portal</div>
      <h1>We've received<br>your <span>application.</span></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="body">

      <p class="greeting">
        Hello <strong>{{ $json.name }}</strong>,
      </p>

      <p class="message">
        Thank you for submitting your loan application. We've successfully received your request and our team is currently reviewing your details. You'll hear from us shortly with the next steps.
      </p>

      <div class="status-card">
        <p>Application Reference</p>
        <div class="ref">{{ $json.applicant_id }}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-title">What happens next</div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Eligibility Review</strong> — We'll assess your application against our lending criteria within a short period.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Loan Offer</strong> — If eligible, you'll receive a personalised loan offer with your interest rate and repayment breakdown.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-text"><strong>Your Decision</strong> — You'll be able to accept or decline the offer directly from your email — no login required.</div>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <div class="closing">
