        <strong>The LoanDesk Team</strong>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This email was sent because you submitted a loan enquiry at LoanDesk.<br>
        If this wasn't you, please <a href="#">contact us immediately</a>.<br><br>
        &copy; 2026 LoanDesk. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>

